      "en": "Volume 71: Timeline for the Hereditary Houses of the Ten Kingdoms",
      "raw": "卷七十一 十國世家年譜第十一 Volume 71: Timeline for the Hereditary Houses of the Ten Kingdoms"
    },
    "sentenceCount": 81,
    "translatedCount": 0,
